K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-4: de dag la de bzhin du 'jug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-5: de bzhin gshegs pa ni sems can gyi don phun sum tshogs pa la dgyes par mi 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-6: ma 'byor pa la'ang mi dgyes par mi 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-7: yang dag par zhugs pa rnams la ni sgrib pa med pa'i byams pa chen po 'jug /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-8: log par zhugs pa rnams la ni sgrib pa med pa'i thugs rje chen po 'jug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-10: byang chub sems dpas chos kyi tshul la 'jug pa bcu po de dag gis de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi 'jug pa khong du chud par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-12: byang chub sems dpas chos kyi tshul la 'jug pa bcus de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi dpe dang 'dra ba khong du chud par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-16: nyi ma ni sems can tha ma dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:13b-21: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang sems can tha ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-0: ma dad pa thams cad la mtshungs par 'char zhing mtshungs par ye shes snang bar mdzad @14a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-4: nam mkha' ni thams cad du sems can thams cad la mi sgrib pa'i ngo bo nyid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-5: gzhan du na glo bur gyi du ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-7: rdul dang; khug rna dag gis sgrib pa dang bcas par kun tu snang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-8: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa yang nam mkha' ltar sems can thams cad la mi sgrib pa'i ngo bo nyid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-9: gzhan du na glo bur gyi du ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-12: khug rna lta bu'i ngar 'dzin pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-13: nga yir 'dzin pas bsgribs par sems can rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa mthong zhing myong bar mi 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-16: me ni shing thams cad la yod mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-18: rtsol ba ma tshang na mi 'bar zhing rang gi dgos pa rnams mi byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-19: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'ang shes bya thams cad la gnas mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-20: dad pa la sogs pa'i rkyen dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-21: rtsol ba ma tshang na mi 'byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-22: sangs rgyas kyi bya ba rnams kyang mi mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-25: tshon tha dad pa snod gcig gi nang du blugs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14a-26: tshon mang po de'i nang du ras tha gu tha dad pas phur te bcug na phur ma'i dbang ji lta ba bzhin du tshon chags kyang tshon de dag mi rtog /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-0: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa dge ba'i rtsa ba sna tshogs kyi tshogs mang po'ang mos pa'i tha gus ji ltar phur ba bzhin du sems can @14b rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa mthong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan yang len par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-4: chus gang ba'i klung ni bstod kyang dma' bar 'bab po /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-5: zhe sdang zhing ngan du smras kyang dma' bar 'bab pa yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-6: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'ang bstod dam /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-7: ngan du smras kyang ye shes kyis gshegs pa yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-8: nga rgyal gyis gshegs pa ni ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-13: gshags nas 'chos kyang mngar ba'i ro de mi 'dor ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-14: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'ang mchod kyang rung ma mchod kyang rung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-15: bsnyen pa na rnam par grol ba'i mngar ba'i ro de mi 'dor ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-18: sa ni rnam par mi rtog cing 'gyur ba med par gnas te; de la khe 'dod pa gang dag gis rmos nas yongs su sbyang ba byas te sa bon btab pa de dag gi lo tog phun sum tshogs par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-20: yongs su sbyang ba mi byed /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-21: sa bon mi 'debs pa de dag gi lo tog ni phun sum tshogs par mi 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-22: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'ang sa ltar rnam par mi rtog cing 'gyur ba med par gnas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-23: de la yon tan 'dod pa gang dag de bzhin gshegs pa la dad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:14b-25: gus pa bskyed pa de dag gi yon tan gyi lo tog phun sum tshogs par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-1: gshegs pa la dad pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-3: gus pa mi bskyed pa de dag gi yon tan gyi lo tog ni phun sum tshogs par mi 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-6: la la zhig gis tsandan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-7: ga pur la mi snyan pa byas te ngan du brjod nas rang gi lus la bskus kyang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-9: ga pur de dri zhim par byed kyi dri nga bar mi byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-10: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyang ngan du smra ste mi snyan pa brjod nas bsnyen cing bsten te bsnyen bkur byed pa de dag de bzhin gshegs pas sangs rgyas kyi yon tan gyi dri dang ldan par mdzad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-15: khri lam ni sems can tha ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-17: mchog thams cad la mi thogs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-18: bde bar 'gro bar byed pas mtshungs par gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-19: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'ang sems can tha ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-21: mchog thams cad la mi mnyam pa med cing sgrib pa med pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-22: bde bar 'gro bas mtshungs par 'jug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-25: ri'i rgyal po gangs ri la rtsi'i rgyal po mthong na mdzes pa zhes bya ba yod de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15a-26: de mthong ma thag tu sems can thams cad kyi nad thams cad med par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-0: de bzhin du de bzhin gshegs pa'ang @15b mthong ma thag tu sems can thams cad kyi nad thams cad sel bar 'gyur te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-4: byang chub sems dpas chos kyi tshul la 'jug pa bcus sangs rgyas khong du chud par bya ste /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-16: mdun du gzhag pa'i sangs rgyas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-17: de la rgyu mthun pa'i sangs rgyas gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-18: gang pha rol tu phyin pa rnams kyi rgyu mthun pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-19: pha rol tu phyin pa'i chos sgrub par byed pa yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-20: 'di gnyis las gang grub pa de ni sgrub pa'i sangs rgyas te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-21: de'i phyir rgyu mthun pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:15b-22: de la rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i sangs rgyas gang zhe na /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:16a-3: 'di ni rnam par smin pa las byung ba'i sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:16a-7: 'di ni ting nge 'dzin gyi sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:17a-0: dbang thob cing snying rje chen pos bskul bas sangs rgyas kyi gzugs su sprul nas sems @17a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:17a-1: can rnams 'dul ba 'di ni sprul pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:17a-2: de la btags pa'i sangs rgyas gang zhe na /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:17a-7: yongs su bsgrub pa 'di ni btags pa'i sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:17b-24: de bzhin du khams ston pa dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:18a-3: de ni chos tsam du zad pas sems can med do //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:18a-14: de'i phyir las gang la'ang byed pa med do //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:18a-22: skye bas gzir bar 'gyur ba de'ang med par 'gyur te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33a-24: dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams kyi gzugs brnyan du gyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33a-25: sngar ldang zhing bsam pa dge ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33a-27: mig rig rig byas pas don go ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-0: 'khor los bsgyur ba phal gzhan @33b rnams kyi lta bu ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-1: de la sogs pa 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rin po che ba bkod pa thams cad sprul nas byang chub sems dpa' sems la dbang ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-2: sems can thams cad la phan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-3: bde ba'i lhag pa'i bsam pa can /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-4: mi rin po che kha na ma tho ba med pa'i las zab pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-6: phan pa'i lhag pa'i bsam pa dam pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-7: chos chen po la gzhol ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-9: dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam la bsten pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-10: skyes bu chen po'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pas sems can rnams yongs su smin par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-11: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor los bsgyur bar 'phrul pa chen po zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-12: nam 'jig rten na brgya byin gtso bor byed pa de na brgya byin gyi gzugs su sprul nas sum cu rtsa gsum gyi khang par zhugs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-13: bag yod pa'i gtam gyis lha rnams yongs su smin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-14: nam 'jig rten na tshangs pa gtso bor byed pa de na tshangs pa'i gzugs su sprul nas rab tu zhi ba'i bsam gtan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-15: tshad med pa'i bsam gtan rnams kyis tshangs pa'i ris kyi lha rnams yongs su smin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-16: nam sems can rnams nyan thos kyis 'dul ba yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-17: rang sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:33b-18: sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba ma yin pa de na nyan thos kyi gzugs su sprul nas sdug bsngal zad par bya ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-1: 'das pa thob par bya ba'i phyir chos ston to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-2: nam sems can rnams rang sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-3: nyan thos kyis 'dul ba ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-4: sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba ma yin pa de na rang sangs rgyas kyi gzugs su sprul nas rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub kyi lam yang dag par rab tu ston te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-6: 'dod chags dang bral ba'i gtam dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-11: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa'i gtam dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-12: sbyin gnas chen por dbang skur ba'i gtam dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-14: rnam par thar pa'i tshul gyis sems can rnams yongs su smin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-15: nam sems can rnams byang chub sems dpas 'dul bar 'gyur pa de na rang gi gzugs su gnas nas pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-22: sa'i gtam gyis sems can de dag yongs su smin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-23: nam sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba'i sems can dbang po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-24: khams rgya che zhing rgyas par gyur pa de na sangs rgyas kyi gzugs su bsgyur nas stobs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34a-26: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa'i gtam rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-0: sangs rgyas kyi rdzu @34b 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul chen po rnams kyis sems can de dag yongs su smin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-1: nam sems can rnams sangs rgyas kyi zhing rgya chen pos 'dul bar 'gyur ba de na stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams lag mthil ltar mnyam pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-3: ka tsa lindi ka ltar reg na bde ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-4: bee d'urya sngon por gyur la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-6: tsandan sprul gyi snying por gyur pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-7: dzambu chu bo'i gser du gyur pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-12: ngan song log par ltung ba med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-13: bud med rgyu ba med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-15: rin po che sna tshogs kyi ri rnams kyis mdzes par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-19: rin po che'i shing ljon pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-20: spos kyi shing sna tshogs kyis mdzes par byas pa sprul nas sems can de dag yongs su smin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-21: nam sems can rnams byang chub kyi snying po rgya chen pos 'dul bar 'gyur ba de na byang chub kyi shing dpag tshad bcu gnyis kyi tshad du mngon par sprul te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-22: rtsa ba shin tu zug pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-23: sdong po ni dzambu'i chu bo'i gser /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-28: rin po che tha dad pa; rin po che sna tshogs kyi lo mas mdzes par byas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:34b-29: lha'i bu mo brgya stong du ma gnas pa sprul nas sems can de dag yongs su smin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-1: 'khor rgya chen pos 'dul bar gyur pa de na lha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-7: mi'am ci dang; lto 'phye chen po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-10: 'jig rten skyong ba gzi brjid che ba gzi brjid che ba sprul /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-11: nyan thos so so yang dag par rig pa thob pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-12: gnyis ka'i cha las rnam par grol ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-13: byang chub sems dpa'i sa bcu la gnas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-14: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin thob pa rnams sprul nas sems can de dag yongs su smin par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-16: chos kyi tshul la 'jug pa bcu po de dag gis byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi 'phrul pa chen po khong du chud par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-18: byang chub sems dpas chos kyi tshul la 'jug pa bcus dge ba rnams kyi rnam par smin pa'i dbang pa khong du chud par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-22: chu zla ni nam mkha'i zla ba'i gzugs brnyan yin mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-23: chu zla ni yod pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-24: de bzhin du dge ba mngon par 'du byed pa'i rkyen las rnam par smin pa dge ba sna tshogs yid du 'ong ba 'byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35a-25: ji ltar nam mkha'i zla ba chu'i nang du mi 'pho ba de bzhin du dge ba'i las kyi srid pa 'du byed rnams kyang srid pa 'du byed rnams su 'pho ba'ang ma yin la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-0: @35b las kyi srid pa'i rkyen las kyang srid pa'i rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid kyang 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-3: rma bya'i mdongs gcig las srog chags rnams la gzugs du mar snang ngo /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-4: de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi dge ba mngon par 'du bya ba gcig las rnam par smin pa rnam pa du mar snang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-5: las kyi srid pa'i 'du byed de dag rma bya'i mdongs su mi 'pho mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-6: de'i rkyen las rma bya'i mdongs kyi rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid kyang 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-7: de bzhin du dge ba'i las kyi srid pa bsags pa'ang srid par 'pho ba ma yin yang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-8: dge ba'i las kyi srid pa la brten nas yang srid pa'i rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid kyang 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-11: shin tu ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i dge ba mngon par 'du bya ba mngon par 'du byed pas nam mkha' las me tog gi char 'bab cing me tog de dag gzugs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-12: dri la sogs par dbang ba nyid du 'gyur yang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-13: gang dge ba'i rtsa ba ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba byas pa de dag nam mkha'i me tog de dag tu mi 'pho ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-14: ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i mtshan nyid kyang gzhan la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-15: me tog de dag gi mtshan nyid kyang gzhan no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-16: de bzhin du dge ba'i las kyi srid pa yang yang srid pa'i dge bar 'pho ba'ang ma yin la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:35b-17: dge ba'i las kyi srid pa'i las kyi rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid kyang 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-1: tu chos spyod pa rnams la sil snyan rnams ma bskyod par mchod pa'i las kyi phyir rang sgra 'byung yang chos spyod pa de sil snyan rnams su 'pho ba ma yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-2: chos spyod pa'i mtshan nyid kyang gzhan la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-3: sil snyan de dag gi mtshan nyid kyang gzhan mod kyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-4: chos spyod pa'i rkyen gyis sil snyan rnams ma bskyod par rang sgra 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-5: de bzhin du rab tu byas pa'i dge ba'i las kyi srid pa'i 'du byed rnams yang srid pa'i 'du byed rnams su 'pho ba ma yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-6: rab tu chos spyod pa'i rkyen gyis rab tu'ang srid pa'i rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid kyang 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-9: 'byung ba chen po'i dbang gis nam mkha' la 'ja' 'byung yang der 'byung ba chen po rnams 'pho ba'ang ma yin la; 'byung ba chen po'i rkyen gyis 'ja'i gzugs kyi rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid kyang 'byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-10: de la gang kha dog skya bor snang ba de ni sa'i khams kyi dbang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-11: de la gang kha dog sngon por snang ba de ni chu'i khams kyi dbang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-12: de la gang kha dog dmar por snang ba de ni me'i khams kyi dbang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36a-14: zlum por 'dug pa de ni rlung gi khams kyi dbang ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-0: de bzhin du dge ba'i las kyi 'du byed byas pa rnams kyi dge ba'i las kyi srid pa'i dbang gis yang srid pa'i rnam par smin pa'i @36b dbang ba nyid 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-3: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam gyi sdom pa'i rkyen gyis rin po che sna bdun dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-4: 'bras sa bon ma btab ma rmos par 'byung yang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-5: dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam gyi sdom pa rkyen du gyur pa de rin po che de rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-6: 'bras rnams su 'phos pa'ang ma yin la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-7: dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam gyi sdom pa'i rkyen gyis 'khor los bsgyur ba'i dbang ba nyid kyang 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-8: de bzhin du dge ba legs par byas pa shin tu mthar phyin pa legs par brtsams pa las yang srid pa'i dge ba'i rnam par smin pa 'byung yang las kyi srid pa'ang srid par 'pho ba ma yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-9: de'i phyir rnam par smin pa mi 'dra ba zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-12: lha rab tu dge ba dang ldan pa rnams kyi me tog mand'a ra ba bskyed mi dgos pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-13: gzhal med khang bya mi dgos pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-14: bdud rtsi'i zas bsgrub mi dgos par 'byung yang dge ba'i 'du byed kyi las kyi rnam par smin pa de dag 'pho ba ma yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-15: dge ba'i 'du byed kyi rkyen gyis lha'i rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:36b-18: rdzu 'phrul chen po rnams kyi rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du byed pa'i rkyen gyis sgrib pa med par dbang ba nyid 'byung yang rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du byed pa sgrib pa med par 'pho ba'ang ma yin la /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-1: 'du byed pa'i rkyen gyis rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa rnams kyi sgrib pa med pa'ang 'byung ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-2: ri la sogs pa 'pho ba'ang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-3: bsams pa tsam gyis sgrib pa med par 'byung ba'ang ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-4: de bzhin du bag yod pa rnams kyi dge ba mngon par 'du byed pa'i rkyen gyis yang srid pa'i rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid 'byung ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-7: rlung gi rkyen gyis me 'byung gi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-9: me byung nas tshos par bya bar snang ba la sogs par rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid 'byung yang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-10: me'i dbang ba de rlung dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-12: me la me'i dbang ba nyid yod pa'ang ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-13: de bzhin du rkyen thams cad las skyes pa'i dge ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-14: mi dge ba'i rnam par smin pa'ang so sor khong du chud par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-17: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dge slong dge ba zad pa med pa'i tshogs rnam par dag pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-18: dbang rab tu thob pas zad par nam mkha' bsams pa tsam gyis de bzhin du 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-24: ser po dang; dmar po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-25: dkar po rnams kyi sgrib pa med par 'gyur yang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37a-26: sems kyi sgrib pa med pa nam mkha'i sgrib pa med par 'pho ba'ang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-0: bsams pa tsam gyis @37b sgrib pa med par 'gyur ba yang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-1: sems kyi sgrib pa med pa de dang mi ldan par sra ba la sogs pa'i sgrib pa med par 'gyur ba yang ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-2: de bzhin du rkyen las byung ba'i dge ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-3: mi dge ba thams cad kyi rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid khong du chud par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-4: byang chub sems dpas chos kyi tshul la 'jug pa bcu po de dag gis dge ba rnams kyi rnam par smin pa'i dbang ba nyid khong du chud par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-6: byang chub sems dpas chos kyi tshul la 'jug pa bcus zag pa med pa'i dge ba rnams kyi rnam par smin pa 'thob pa'i dbang ba nyid khong du chud par bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-9: mngon par shes pa drug dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-11: rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-12: zil gyis gnon pa'i skye mched brgyad dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-13: zad par gyi skye mched bcu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-16: mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-19: de la mngon par shes pa drug gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-22: pha rol gyi sems shes pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-23: sngon gyi gnas rjes su dran pa'i shes pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-24: rdzu 'phrul bya ba shes pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-25: zag pa zad pa shes pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:37b-26: 'di dag ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi mngon par shes pa drug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-1: dpa'i lha'i mig gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-2: dge ba'i tshogs thams cad bsags pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-11: kha na ma tho ba med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-14: rang sangs rgyas rnams dang thun mong ma yin pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-15: bag chags kyi mtshams sbyor pa thams cad yang dag par bcom pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-17: phyad par lung ston pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-18: lha'i mig des sems can rnams mthong ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-25: las nye bar 'gro ba ji lta ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-27: rnam par smin pa dang bcas pa yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-28: de'i lha'i mig de ni sangs rgyas kyi ye shes thob par byed pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-30: de la byang chub sems dpa'i lha'i rna ba ni de lha'i rna ba sgrib pa med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-31: dge ba'i tshogs thams cad bsags pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38a-32: byis pa so so'i skye bo dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-0: @38b lto 'phye chen po thams cad dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-2: rang sangs rgyas thams cad las khyad par du 'phags pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-3: chod pa med pa 'od gsal bas sgra thams cad thos te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-16: 'phags pa ma yin pa'i sgra rnams kyang thos te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-17: thos nas kyang 'phags pa ma yin pa'i sgra rnams la khong khro bar yang mi byed /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-18: 'phags pa'i sgra rnams la rjes su chags par yang mi byed /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-19: so so'i skye bo'i sgra rnams la tha mar 'du shes pa'ang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-21: rang sangs rgyas kyi sgra rnams la dam par 'du shes pa'ang ma yin; 'phags pa ma yin pa'i tshul la khong khro bar yang mi byed /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-22: 'phags pa'i tshul la rjes su chags par yang mi byed /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:38b-23: sgra gang la'ang yon tan du 'du shes pa'am /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-11: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis bdag med pa'i mtshan nyid du shes nas nges par gyur pa la 'jug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-12: mtshan nyid las gyur pa'i nges par gyur pa ni mtshan nyid kyi bden pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-13: de bzhin du chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis zhi ba'i mtshan nyid dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-14: rang bzhin gyis dben pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-15: rang bzhin gyis stong pa'i mtshan nyid dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-16: rang bzhin gyis mi skye mi 'gag pa'i mtshan nyid du shes nas nges par gyur pa la 'jug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-17: mtshan nyid las gyur pa'i nges par gyur pa ni mtshan nyid kyi bden pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-18: de la rnam par dbye ba'i mtshan nyid ni chos thams cad mtshan nyid gcig pa las gzhan gyi dbang gis rnam par phye ste bstan pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-19: mtshan nyid gcig ces bya ba ni stong pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:48b-20: de ltar chos thams cad stong pa nyid dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-1: 'di ni stong pa nyid de'i rnam par dbye ba ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-2: rnam par dbye ba de dag thams cad kyang stong pa nyid kyi mtshan nyid do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-3: de ltar stong pa nyid la slu bar mi phyed pa de'i phyir rnam par dbye ba'i bden pa zhes bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-4: 'di ni rnam par dbye ba'i bden pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-5: de la phye ste rtog pa'i bden pa gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-6: phral nas rtog pa ni phye ste rtog pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-11: shes pa shes bya la mi slu ba ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-12: de'i phyir phye ste rtog pa'i bden pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-13: de la dngos po'i bden pa ni dngos po shes pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-14: dngos po de dag ni phung po dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-19: skye mched de dag rten cing 'brel par 'byung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-21: dngos po med par shes pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-22: de ltar shes nas nges par gyur pa la 'jug pas de'i phyir dngos po'i bden pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-23: de la nus pa'i bden pa ni ye shes de dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-25: lam des nyon mongs pa spong bar byed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-28: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa khong du chud pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-29: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dbang po nyid khong du chud par nus pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49a-30: de'i phyir nus pa'i bden pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-0: mi skye ba shes pa'i bden pa ni 'dus byas @49b thams cad zad pa can du ston te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-1: zad pa de'ang mi zad pa zad pa la zad pa med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-2: gal te zad pa la zad pa yod du zin na 'gog ba'ang zad par 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-3: de'i phyir zad pa zad par mi 'gyur ro; ;gang zad par mi 'gyur ba de mi skye ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-5: mi skye ba shes pa'i bden pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-6: de la lam la 'jug pa shes pa'i bden pa gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-7: ye shes kyi lam bsod nams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-8: ye shes kyi tshogs bsags pa gang gis chos thams cad ma skyes ma 'gags par shes pa des 'jug cing 'dzud pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-9: de'i phyir lam la 'jug pa shes pa'i bden pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-10: de la de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kun 'byung ba'i bden pa gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-12: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sa'i bar ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kun 'byung ba'i bden pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-13: de bstan pa'i lam gyis mngon par rtogs pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-14: 'di dag ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi bden pa bcu'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-15: de la byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi mthar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-16: 'di la byang chub sems dpa' ni 'dod pa dag las dben pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-17: sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos rnams las dben pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-18: rtog pa dang bcas pa; dpyod pa dang bcas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-19: dben pa las skyes pa'i dga' ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:49b-20: bde ba can bsam gtan dang po rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-0: de la 'dod pa rnams ni bsam gtan dang po'i mi @50a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-2: gang sred pa de dag las dben pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-3: de la sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos rnams ni chags pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-6: gzhi de las srog gcod pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-7: ma byin par len pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-8: 'dod pa la log par g-yem pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-16: 'di ni sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos rnams zhes bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-17: de dag las dben pa ni bsam gtan dang po'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-18: rtog pa dang lhan cig pa ni rtog pa dang bcas pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-19: rtog pa de dag gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-20: gang dag bsam gtan dang po dang mthun pa'i rtog pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-21: de cho ga bzhin du rtog cing de dag kyang dul bas na de dag ni rtog pa zhes bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-26: ting nge 'dzin du byed pa ni rtog pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-27: de la dpyod pa gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-28: bsam gtan dang po dang mthun pa'i rtog pa de dag nyid la dbyod pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-31: kun tu longs spyod pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-32: ting nge 'dzin du byed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-33: sems rjes su 'gro ba ni dpyod pa zhes bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-34: de dag dang lhan cig pa ni rtog pa dang bcas pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50a-35: dpyod pa dang bcas pa bsam gtan dang po'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-0: bde ba dben pa las skyes pas de'i phyir dben @50b pa las skyes pa'i dga' ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-2: rdzogs pa'i byas te gnas zhes bya ba la rdzogs par byas zhes bya ba ni sdom pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-8: bsam gtan dang po de la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa khong du chud par bya ba'i 'dun pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-10: de mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa'i 'dun pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-11: 'dod pa des bsam gtan dang po la snying por 'du shes pa yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-12: de bsam gtan gnyis pa la rtsom ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-13: de bsam gtan dang po'i rtog pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-14: dpyod pa de dag zhi bar byed /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-16: de dag las sems rab tu zhi bar byed cing bsam gtan gnyis pa yongs su 'grub pa'i rgyu tshol te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-18: dpyod pa dang bral bas nang yongs su dvang ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-19: sems kyi rgyud gcig tu gyur pas rtog pa med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-21: dga' ba dang ldan pa bsam gtan gnyis pa rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-22: de la nang yongs su dvang ba ni de'i bsam gtan gnyis pa'i mi mthun pa'i phyogs kyi chos gang yin pa de dag nye bar zhi ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-24: de'i phyir nang yongs sa dang ba zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-25: rgyud gcig tu gyur ces bya ba ni bsam gtan dang po'i rtog pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:50b-26: dpyod pa de dag thams cad rab tu zhi nas rgya mtsho'i chu ltar ro gcig tu 'gyur ba 'thob pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-2: rgya mtsho chen por chu 'bab pa rnams ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-4: lan tshva'i ror ro gcig par 'gyur ba de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa' bsam gtan gnyis pa la snyoms par zhugs pa'i bsam gtan dang po'i rtog pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-5: dpyod pa de dag thams cad zhi nas ro gcig tu 'gyur te de ting nge 'dzin ces bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-6: ting nge 'dzin de las de sangs rgyas dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-8: dge 'dun la dga' ba skye ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-9: de dkon mchog gsum la dga' bas dge ba'i chos rnams rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-10: de las mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa'i 'dun pa shin tu 'bar ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-12: shin tu yid du 'ong ba 'thob bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-13: de mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa la 'dun pa des bsam gtan gnyis pa de la mi chags te bsam gtan gsum pa kun tu tshol lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-15: dga' ba ni bsam gtan gsum pa'i sgrib pa yin no snyam nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-16: de dga' ba de las 'dod chags dang bral nas btang snyoms can dran pa yongs su dag pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-17: 'phags pa rnams kyis gang de dga' ba med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-18: bde ba la gnas pa zhes brjod pa bsam gtan gsum pa rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51a-19: ting nge 'dzin de las skyes pa'i dga' ba la 'dod chags dang bral ba thob pa de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-0: gang de dga' ba med pa'i bde ba de ni @51b gtan du bde ba ma yin gyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-1: zad pa'i chos can 'jig pa'i chos can te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-2: de mi rtag cing mi brtan la ther zug ma yin zhing de yid brtan du mi rung ngo snyam pa'i sems de lta bu 'thob bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-3: de de ltar shes nas mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa rab tu 'thob pa'i 'dun pa drag po chen po 'thob pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-4: de mi skye ba'i chos kyi 'dun pa drag po des bde ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-5: sdug bsngal la mngon par chags pa mi skye'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-6: de bde ba'ang spangs te snga nas sdug bsngal yang spangs shing /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-8: yid mi bde ba'ang nub pas bde ba'ang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-9: sdug bsngal ba'ang ma yin pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-11: dran pa yongs su dag pa bsam gtan bzhi pa rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-12: de bsam gtan bzhi pa la snyoms par zhugs pas mnyen pa'i sems so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-14: las su rung ba'i sems so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-17: bde ba de sems can thams cad kyis mngon par sman to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-18: de sems can thams cad la phan pa dang bde ba la mngon du phyogs pas mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa'i snang ba skye'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-19: de mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa'i snang ba skyes pa des bsam gtan bzhi pa sdug bsngal yang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-20: bde ba'ang ma yin pa mang ba de la dga' bar mi 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:51b-22: dran pa yongs su dag pa'i bde ba de la'ang chags par mi byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-1: pas de la nam mkha' nyid snang bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-2: de thams cad tu gzugs kyi 'du shes rnams las yang dag par 'das te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-3: thogs pa'i 'du shes rnams nub par gyur cing sna tshogs kyi 'du shes rnams yid la mi byed pas nam mkha' mtha' yas so snyam nas nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-5: mdor na 'di la gzugs ni rnam pa gnyis te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-8: de la 'byung ba'i gzugs ni sa'i khams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-9: chu'i khams dang; me'i khams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-11: 'byung ba las gyur pa'i gzugs ni kha dog dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-15: de ltar gzugs rnam pa brgyad do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-16: gzugs de dag gi 'du shes rnams las yang dag par 'das nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-17: thogs pa'i 'du shes mi 'byung ste nub par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-18: gang gzugs su 'du shes pa de ni thogs par 'du shes pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-19: de bas na gzugs kyi 'du shes rnams las yang dag par 'das nas thogs pa'i 'du shes rnams nub par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-20: thogs pa'i 'du shes rnams nub pa sna tshogs kyi 'du shes rnams yid la byed pa mi 'jug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52a-21: sna tshogs kyi 'du shes rnams yid la mi byed pas nam mkha' mtha' yas so snyam du 'jug go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-0: de nam mkha' mtha' yas so snyam @52b nas nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-1: de la byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched la snyoms par zhugs pa 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-2: nam mkha' ni mtha' med pas mtha' yas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-3: gang la mtha' med pa de'i thog ma yod par ga la 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-4: dbus yod par ga la 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-5: de ltar chos thams cad ni thog ma dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-8: de ltar snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems can rnams la ni snying rje chen po bskyed /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-9: chos rnams la ni nam mkha' dang mtshungs pa nyid kyi shes pa 'jug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-10: de ni don de'i mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa rtsom pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-11: de rnam pa thams cad du nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched las yang dag par 'das te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-12: rnam par shes pa mtha' yas so snyam nas rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-14: gang nam mkha' 'du shes pa 'di ni rnam par shes par 'gyur ba'o snyam nas de 'di snyam du 'di thams cad du rnam par shes pa tsam ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-15: rnam shes mtha' yas de'ang yod pa'ang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-16: med pa'ang ma yin no snyam du sems so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-17: de de ltar snyoms par zhugs pas mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:52b-18: yongs su grub pa ni ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-0: de rnam pa thams cad du rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched las yang dag par @53a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-1: 'das te ci'ang med do snyam nas ci'ang med pa'i skye mched rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-2: ci'ang med ces bya ba la ci'ang zhes bya ba ni 'dod chags dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-3: zhe sdang dang; gti mug dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-7: 'dus byas kyi chos thams cad yang dag pa ma yin pa kun tu rtog pa las byung ba rnams ni ci'ang med zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-8: ci'ang med pa ni ji skad du brjod pa de dag las chung ngur gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-9: phra bar gyur pa ni ci'ang med pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-10: de la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa ni shin tu 'bar ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-11: shin tu 'od gsal ba yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-15: thob pa de'i phyir ci'ang med pa'i skye mched la mi chags te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-17: de gong du rtsol ba na 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-18: 'di ni gang 'du byed rnams kyi phra ba la ci'ang med par yongs su brtags pa ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-19: de ni 'du shes med 'du shes med pa'ang ma yin no snyam mo; ;de la 'du shes med pa ni stong pa'i phyir ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-20: 'du shes med pa'ang ma yin pa ni rten cing 'brel bar byung ba'i phyir ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-21: de 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched mngon du 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-22: de rnam pa thams cad du ci'ang med pa'i skye mched las yang dag par 'das te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53a-23: 'du shes med 'du shes med min skye mched rdzogs par byas te gnas so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53b-0: @53b gang la gnas nas 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53b-1: gang la 'du shes med 'du shes med min de la dga' ba ci zhig yod snyam nas de blo de las gong du bskyod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53b-2: de blo de las gong du bskyod nas skye ba med pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:53b-3: 'gag pa med pa'i chos mngon du 'gyur te /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:77b-19: chos ni thams cad du 'dod pa med pas chos ni sdang ba rnams la zhe 'gras pa'ang med /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:77b-20: dad pa rnams la rjes su chags pa'ang med de; de ltar bdag gis kyang chos dang 'dra ba'i sems su bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:77b-21: chos ni bri ba'ang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:77b-24: grangs med pas nam mkha' ltar 'bri ba'ang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-1: de ltar bdag gis kyang chos dang 'dra ba'i sems su bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-2: chos ni sems can rnams kyis bsrung ba ma yin gyi chos kyis sems can rnams bsrung ba ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-3: de ltar bdag gis kyang chos dang 'dra ba'i sems su bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-4: chos ni skyabs yongs su tshol ba ma yin pas chos ni 'jig rten thams cad kyi skyabs yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-5: de ltar bdag gis kyang chos dang 'dra ba'i sems su bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-6: chos ni thogs pa med pa'i mtshan nyid pas chos ni gang la'ang thogs pa med de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-7: de ltar bdag gis kyang chos dang 'dra ba'i sems su bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-8: chos ni bag la nyal med pas bag la nyal la mi 'jug ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-9: de ltar bdag gis kyang chos dang 'dra ba'i sems su bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-10: chos ni rtag tu rnam par mi rtog pas chos ni 'khor bas 'jigs skrag pa'ang ma yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-11: mya ngan las 'das pa la rjes su chags pa'ang ma yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-12: de ltar bdag gis kyang chos dang 'dra ba'i sems su bya'o snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-13: de ltar na byang chub sems dpa' chos la chos ltar dran pa nye bar 'jog pas de'i phyir chos rjes su dran pa zhes bya ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-15: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i chos rjes su dran pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-16: de la byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun rjes su dran pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78a-17: 'di la byang chub sems dpa' 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-7: chos kyi bya ba byed pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-9: chos spyod pa phun sum tshogs pa; rang bzhin gyis drang ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-13: rtag tu dpen pa spyod yul ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-14: rtag tu chos la gzhol ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-15: rtag tu dkar po spyod pa'o snyam mo; ;gzhan yang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-16: byang chub sems dpa' 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-17: bcom ldan 'das kyis dge 'dun rnam pa du mar gsungs pa ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-21: ngo tsha shes pa'i dge 'dun dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-22: ngo tsha med pa'i dge 'dun dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-25: phyir mi ldog pa'i dge 'dun no snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-26: de la byang chub sems dpa' ni kun rdzob kyi dge 'dun bsdu ba'i phyir nan tan byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-27: don dam pa'i dge 'dun la bsten pa'i phyir nan tan byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-28: ngo tsha shes pa'i dge 'dun rnam par thar bar bya ba'i phyir nan tan byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-29: ngo tsha med pa'i dge 'dun yongs su gdul ba'i phyir nan tan byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-30: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun la mchod cing bsti stang bya ba'i phyir nan tan byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-31: cang shes kyi dge 'dun la sangs rgyas bzhin du nan tan byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:78b-32: phyir mi ldog pa'i dge 'dun la chos kyi gtam gyi phyir nan tan byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-0: gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' 'di snyam @79a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-2: rigs 'dzin pa'i phyir sangs rgyas kyi sras rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-3: yid du 'ong ba'i 'bras bu rab tu sbyin pa'i phyir zhing bzang po rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-4: gnas ngan len dang bral ba'i phyir 'jigs pa med pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-5: yongs su 'dzin pa gtong zhing 'dor ba'i phyir sems rnam par grol ba rnams kyi dge 'dun no; ;shin tu dul ba'i phyir cang shes pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-6: ma 'dres pa'i phyir nyon mongs pa med pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-7: sdig pa dang bral ba'i phyir ngo tsha shes pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-8: bka' blo bde ba'i phyir slob ma rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-9: bdag yongs su shes pa dang ldan pa'i phyir bdag gis med pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-10: zhi ba'i phyir rgyags pa med pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-11: 'dod pa nyung ba'i phyir phyin ci ma log pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-12: rnam par rtog pa yang dag par chad pa'i phyir nad med pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no; ;pha rol tu son pa'i phyir thang la gnas pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-13: thang la gnas pa'i phyir bde ba thob pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-14: de kho na mthong ba'i phyir bag yod pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-15: skyon ma chags pa'i phyir dgon pa pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79a-16: rgya che ba'i phyir byang chub la gzhol ba rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-0: bslab pa gsum gyis bya ba shes @79b par bya ba'i phyir bslab pa 'dod pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-1: dran pa nye bar gzhag pa spyod yul ba'i phyir dran pa dang ldan pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-2: yang dag par spong ba spyod yul ba'i phyir brtson 'grus brtsams pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-3: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa spyod yul ba'i phyir ngal ba med pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-4: dbang po spyod yul ba'i phyir mi phyed pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no; ;stobs spyod yul ba'i phyir tsher ma dkrugs pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-5: byang chub kyi yan lag spyod yul ba'i phyir bsgrib pa med pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-6: lam spyod yul ba'i phyir yang dag par lta ba rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-7: bden pa spyod yul ba'i phyir 'phags pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-8: bsam gtan spyod yul ba'i phyir mnyam par bzhag pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-9: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba spyod yul ba'i phyir chos kyi 'khor lo rab tu bskor ba rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-10: snying rje chen po dang ldan pa'i phyir phyir mi ldog pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-11: bsod nams thams cad kyi tshogs bsags pa'i phyir skye ba gcig gis thogs pa rnams kyi dge 'dun no snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-12: de la byang chub sems dpa' 'di ltar dge 'dun rjes su dran pas 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:79b-13: gang dge 'dun gyi yang dag pa'i yon tan de dag ni bdag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-0: sems can thams cad kyis kyang bsgrub par bya'o snyam pa 'di ni byang chub sems @80a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-1: dpa'i dge 'dun rjes su dran pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-2: de la byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims rjes su dran pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gang zhe na; 'di la byang chub sems dpa' 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-4: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i phun sum tshogs pa gang ci yang rung ba de dag thams cad ni tshul khrims las byung bar blta'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-6: tshul khrims ni phun sum tshogs pa de dag thams cad kyi gnas yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-11: nags tshal thams cad kyi gnas yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-12: de bzhin du tshul khrims kyang phun sum tshogs pa de dag thams cad kyi gnas yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-13: byang chub sems dpa' tshul khrims kyi gnas la rab tu gnas pa ni lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten gyi sbyin gnas yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-14: sbyin pa'i chos yongs su rdzogs par yang byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-15: tshul khrims kyi gnas la rab tu gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni dga' ba skye'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-16: yid dga' bas 'gyod pa med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-17: 'gyod pa med pas mchog tu dga' ba 'thob bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-18: mchog tu dga' bas lus dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-19: sems shin tu sbyangs par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-21: sems shin tu sbyangs pas bde ste ting nge 'dzin thob bo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80a-22: yid mnyam par bzhag pas yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du mthong ba yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-0: yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du mthong ba'i @80b byang chub sems dpa' ni sems can rnams la snying rje chen po 'jug go snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-1: de yang 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-2: bdag gis sems can thams cad la ting nge 'dzin [?] 'di dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-3: chos rnams yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du mthong ba bsgrub par bya'o snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-4: de snying rje chen po des bskul bas lhag pa'i tshul khrims dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-6: lhag pa'i shes rab la bslab pa yongs su rdzogs nas bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-7: de bas na bdag gis kyang tshul khrims la gnas pa mi bskyod pa mi lhod par bya'o; ;sems can thams cad mngon du byas nas tshul khrims bsrung bar bya'o snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-9: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims de ni sems can thams cad la phan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-10: bde ba'i gnas la mi gnas pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-12: byang chub sems dpa' 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-13: byang chub sems dpa'i mngon par 'byung ba'i tshul khrims ni gnod sems med pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-14: byang chub sems dpa'i rab tu byung ba'i tshul khrims ni bdog pa thams cad yongs su gtong ba rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-15: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa dang sdom pa yang dag par 'dzin pa'i tshul khrims ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:80b-18: sems yongs su dag pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-0: byang chub sems dpa'i nges par sems pa'i @81a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-1: tshul khrims ni mngon par shes pa drug yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-2: byang chub sems dpa'i nang du yang dag 'jog pa'i tshul khrims ni byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos rnams yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-3: byang chub sems dpa'i chos nyan pa'i tshul khrims ni so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-4: byang chub sems dpa'i thos pa yongs su tshol ba'i tshul khrims ni nga rgyal med pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-5: byang chub sems dpa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen la bsnyen bkur byed pa'i tshul khrims ni yon tan gyi chos thams cad chud mi za ba yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-6: byang chub sems dpa'i pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul khrims ni thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-7: byang chub sems dpa'i ji ltar thos pa'i chos rnams ston pa'i tshul khrims ni chos smra ba nyid yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-8: byang chub sems dpa'i ji ltar thos pa'i chos rnams sems dpa'i tshul khrims ni gzungs dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-9: spobs pa thob pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81a-10: byang chub sems dpa'i byang chub kyi sems kyi tshul khrims ni skye ba thams cad las yang dag par 'da' ba yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-0: byang chub sems dpa'i sems can thams cad la khong khro ba med pa'i tshul khrims ni byang chub kyi sems @81b chud mi za bar yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-1: byang chub sems dpa'i byang chub kyi sems chud mi za ba'i tshul khrims ni dkon mchog gsum chud mi za ba yongs su rdzogs par byed do snyam mo; ;de'ang 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-2: tshul khrims bsrungs pas bsrung ba thams cad bsrungs pa yin no snyam pa 'di ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-4: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims rjes su dran pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-5: de la byang chub sems dpa'i gtong ba rjes su dran pa'i dran pa nye bar gzhag pa gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-6: 'di la byang chub sems dpa' 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-7: gang ci gtong ba de thams cad ni /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-9: zang zing gi gtong ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-11: gtong ba rnam pa gnyis kyi nang du 'dus so snyam mo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-12: de la zang zing gi gtong bas ni byang chub sems dpa'i mtshan dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-13: dpe byad bzang po yongs su skor ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-14: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-15: sems can yongs su smin par byed pa rnam par dag pa yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-16: chos kyi gtong bas ni stobs bcu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-18: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-19: bag chags kyang yang dag par 'joms par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-21: zang zing gi gtong bas ni phung po thams cad nges par 'dor bar byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:81b-22: chos kyi gtong bas ni nyan thos dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-1: cad kyi sa las yang dag par 'da'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-3: zang zing gi gtong bas ni skye ba'i lus yongs su sbyong bar byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-4: chos kyi gtong bas ni chos kyi sku yongs su sbyong bar byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-7: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po zang zing gi gtong bas ni pha ma las byung ba'i stobs sgrub par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-8: stobs de ni de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-9: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams ma gtogs par su la'ang med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-10: chos kyi gtong bas ni rdzu 'phrul gyi stobs sgrub par byed de /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-11: stobs de ni de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-12: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams ma gtogs par su la'ang med do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-14: zang zing gi gtong bas ni yongs su smin par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-15: chos kyi gtong bas ni rnam par thar bar byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-17: zang zing gi gtong bas ni tshogs gsag go /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-18: chos kyi gtong bas ni sgrol lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-20: zang zing gi gtong bas ni nor yongs su gtong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-21: chos kyi gtong bas ni thams cad gtong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-23: zang zing gi gtong bas ni nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa las rnam par grol ba sgrub par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-24: chos kyi gtong bas ni shes bya'i sgrib pa las rnam par grol ba sgrub par byed do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82a-26: gtong ba gtong ba zhes bya ba 'di ni yongs su rtog pa gtong ba'i tshig bla dvags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-0: yongs @82b su rtog pa gtong ba de ni gtong ba rnams kyi dam pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-2: yongs su rtog pa btang bas byang chub sems dpa' dag pa zhes bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-5: yongs su rtog pa zhes bya ba 'di gang gi tshig bla dvags /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-8: yongs su rtog pa zhes bya ba 'di ni yang dag pa ma yin zhing med pa las sgro btags pa'i tshig bla dvags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-10: ji ltar na yang dag pa ma yin zhing med pa las sgro btags pa yin /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-12: nam 'di ltar bdag ni chags pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-16: bdag ni rnam par dag pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-20: bdag ni yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'o snyam pa la sogs par sgro btags pa thams cad ni yang dag pa ma yin zhing med pa las yongs su brtags pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-22: 'di dag thams cad ni rgyu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-32: rkyen de dag kyang rang bzhin gyis stong pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-36: yid kyi rnam par shes pa dang bral ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-39: kun nas nyon mongs pa ma yin pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:82b-40: rnam par byang ba ma yin pa /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:83a-29: phongs par 'gyur ba de ma gtogs par byang chub sems dpa' dag sems can rnams la mi sbyin pa gang yang med de /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:83a-32: 'di la byang chub sems dpa' gtong ba phun sum tshogs nas gtong ba chen po byed de /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:83b-4: de la byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi shin tu gtong ba gang zhe na /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:83b-5: 'di la byang chub sems dpa' gtong ba dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92a-8: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis rin po che'i gling chen por phyogs pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas ded dpon lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92a-9: sems can thams cad kyi nyon mongs pa'i nad thams cad gso ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas sman pa lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92a-10: sems can thams cad kyi chos la the tshom za ba'i zug rdu 'don pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas zug rdu 'byin pa lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92b-0: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi phyogs la mkhas pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas gdos pa 'dzin pa lta bur @92b bya'o; ;'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las sems can sgrol ba la mkhas pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas gru lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92b-1: sems can thams cad kyi 'tsho bar gyur pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas stegs bu lta bur bya'o //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92b-4: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che 'dra bar bsam pa thams cad yongs su skong ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92b-5: legs par byas pa'i las byed pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas cang shes su bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92b-6: shes rab zab cing gting dpag dka' ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas rgya mtsho lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92b-7: sangs rgyas kyi byang chub las bsam pa mi g-yo ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas ri rab dang mtshungs par bya'o; ;kun nas mdzes pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas dpag bsam gyi shing lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:92b-8: mthong bar dka' ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas dzambu'i chu bo'i gser 'dra bar bya'o; ;chos la dbang thob pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas brgya byin lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-0: rab tu zhi ba'i spyod lam phun sum tshogs pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas tshangs pa lta bur @93a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-1: bya'o; ;dam pa'i chos yongs su skyong ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas 'jig rten skyong ba lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-2: dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam la bsten pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas 'khor los bsgyur ba lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-3: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi gsang ba 'dzin pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas blon po chen po lta bur bya'o; ;dge sbyong la gnas pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas mngon par 'byung ba la dga' bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-6: sems zhi ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas dge sbyong du bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-12: rnam par grol ba phun sum tshogs pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas dgon pa par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-13: stong pa nyid rtogs pa khong du chud pa'i byang chub sems dpas bsam gtan par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-16: rig sngags 'chang grub pa 'dul ba la mkhas pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas dben pa la mngon par dga' bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-17: rig pa gsum rtogs par khong du chud pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas rig sngags 'chang du bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93a-18: mngon par shes pa drug thob pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas mngon par shes pa'i ye shes su bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-0: @93b skye mched la mkhas pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas mang du thos par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-1: bstan bcos thams cad la mkhas pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas slob dpon du bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-2: zang zing med par chos ston pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas chos smra bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-5: gti mug btul ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas 'dul ba 'dzin par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-6: thams cad du rung ba la tshod shes pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas ma mo 'dzin par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-7: tshol ba thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas dul bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-8: 'dod chags dang bral ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas mi rgod par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-9: zhe sdang dang bral ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas ma khengs par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-10: gti mug dang bral ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas mu cor mi smra bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-11: ngag bsngams pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpa' tshig 'chol bar mi smra bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-12: theg pa chen po la 'dzud pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas ded dpon du bya'o; ;byang chub tu dam bcas pa nyams 'og tu chud pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas khur rtsa ba lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-13: sems can thams cad brten pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas skyed mos tshal 'dra bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:93b-14: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi zong yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas grong khyer lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-0: sems can thams cad la bu gcig pa @94a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-1: bzhin du byams pa dang ldan pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpas phan pa 'dod par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-2: sems can thams cad kyi ci bya ba yongs su thob par bya ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpas bran lta bur bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-5: byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni rma rgod dag la drang ba rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-6: khengs pa dag la nga rgyal med pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-7: g-yo can dag la g-yo med pa rnams yin no //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-9: log par zhugs pa dag la snying rje dang ldan pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-10: ngo tsha med pa dag la ngo tsha dang ldan pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-11: mu cor smra ba dag la khrel yod pa phun sum tshogs pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-12: phas kyi rgol ba thams cad la sems spam gong ba rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-13: 'khor thams cad la bag tsha ba med pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-14: 'jig rten gyi chos thams cad kyis mi gos pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-15: bdud thams cad kyis mi 'phogs pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-16: phas kyi rgol ba thams cad kyis mi thul ba rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-17: bla ma dag la gus pa dang bcas pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-18: 'phags pa dag la zhes dang bcas pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-19: mang du thos pa dag la ri mor byed pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94a-20: bsam gtan dag la ngo mtshar thob pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-0: mkhas pa dag la lhag pa'i bsam pa 'jug @94b pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-1: chos smra ba dag la sangs rgyas tsam du phangs par sems pa dang ldan pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-2: byang chub sems dpa' dag la skyabs su song ba rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-3: sangs rgyas dag la bsam pa thams cad kyis zhugs pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-4: nan tan dag la snying por 'du shes pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-5: nyon mongs pa thams cad kyis mi 'jigs pa rnams yin no; ;snying rje chen po la phyogs pas mya ngan las 'das pa la mi lta ba rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-6: sems can thams cad yongs su smin par byed pa la mngon par dga' bas 'khor ba la phyogs pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-8: bkur sti thams cad la mi lta bas zang zing med par chos ston pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-12: mi gtsang ba yongs su shes pas sems phyin ci ma log pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-13: yul thams cad la mi lta bas sems rnam par grol ba rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-14: 'phags pa'i rigs su skyes pas rigs phun sum tshogs pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-15: rab tu byung ba mang bas blo phun sum tshogs pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-19: lam shes pas 'phags pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:94b-22: bag yod pa la gnas pas skyes bu dam pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-0: 'du byed bdag med par yongs su shes pa dang ldan @95a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-1: pas sems can thams cad la sems mnyam pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-2: 'phags pa'i phyag rgyas btab pas log par mi ltung ba'i chos can rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-3: phyir mi ldog pa'i phyag rgyas btab pas byang chub kyi snying por gzhol ba rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-4: spyod lam mdzes pa phun sum tshogs pas byang chub sems dpa' rtag tu gtsang ma yang dag par spyod pa rnams yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-5: 'jig rten gyi gsang tshig la mngon par dga' ba ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-6: sdig pa'i grogs po la mngon par dga' ba ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-9: tshigs su bcad pa la mngon par dga' ba ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-10: 'du 'dzi dag la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-17: 'thab cing rtsod pa'i gtam la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-24: ri brag ngan pa rnams la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-28: glu la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95a-31: byang chub sems dpa' rnams sems can ser sna can rnams la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-0: mtshams @95b so sor bcad pa rnams dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-1: rgyun sman du gyur pa rnams la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-2: gnod sems kyi tha ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-3: zhe sdang mang ba rnams la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-5: brtson 'grus chung zhing brtson 'grus btang ba rnams la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-6: g-yeng zhing phyin ci log tu gyur la rnam par 'phro ba'i sems la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-8: blun pa lkugs pa'i rang bzhin can rnams la chags pa ma yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-9: byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni chos dang /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-14: gti mug yang dag par chad pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-16: sgra bsnyungs pa la dga' ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-17: tshig mi mang zhing dul ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-18: zhi zhing nye bar zhi ba la dben pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-30: g-ye'i phyogs rnams la mngon par dga' ba yin no //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-33: nye bar zhi ba'i phyogs de dag la rab tu dga' ba yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-34: gnas bcas pa'i phyogs de dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-35: de dag tu nam gyi cha stod dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:95b-36: nam gyi cha smad la mi nyal bar rnal 'byor la brtson par gnas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-1: sgom pa stug po'i mthong na gnas pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-6: bzod pa'i sgo brgya stong la rnam par rgyu ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-7: chos kyi sgo brgya stong dpag tu med pa dag rab tu rnam par 'byed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-8: sangs rgyas brgya stong yang mthong ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-9: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo brgya stong yang thob pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-10: gzungs kyi sgo brgya stong yang mngon du byed pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-11: sems can bye ba khrag khrig brgya stong yang yongs su smin par byed pa de lta bu de dag la mngon par dga' ba yin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-13: byang chub sems dpas de 'dra bar bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-14: de lta bus ni sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi chos nyid khong du chud par nus so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-15: de nas bcom ldan 'das la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rtsom pa med kyis 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-17: theg pa chen po ni bag mchis par gnas shing sgrub pa snying por bgyid pa rnams kyi lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-18: de la sgrub pa ni byang chub tu smon pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-19: bag mchis pa ni smon lam yongs su skong ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-20: gzhan yang sgrub pa ni sbyin pa la sbyor ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-21: bag mchis pa ni rnam par smin pa la mi re ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96a-22: sgrub pa ni tshul khrims kyi sdom pa yang dag par blangs pa ma nyams pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-0: bag mchis pa ni phyir mi ldog pa'i tshul khrims bsgrub @96b pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-1: sgrub pa na bzod pa rtsom pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-2: bag mchis pa ni mi skye ba'i chos rtogs pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-3: sgrub pa ni dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad kun tu tshol bas yongs su mi skye ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-4: bag mchis pa ni rtsom pa thams cad yongs su 'dor ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-5: sgrub pa ni bsam gtan rtsom pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-6: bag mchis pa ni mi gnas pa'i bsam gtan pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-7: sgrub pa ni shes rab yongs su skong ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-8: bag mchis pa ni chos thams cad sprod par mi bgyid pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-9: sgrub pa ni dam pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-10: bag mchis pa ni chos thams cad mi dmigs pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-11: sgrub pa ni sems can rnams byang chub la rab tu 'god pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-12: bag mchis pa ni sems can rnams mi dmigs pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-13: sgrub pa ni dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad bgyis nas byang chub tu yongs su bsngo ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-14: bag mchis pa ni chos thams cad byang chub kyi ngo bo nyid du rtogs pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-15: sgrub pa ni mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-16: bag mchis pa ni bsam bzhin du srid pa yongs su 'dzin pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-17: sgrub pa ni byang chub kyi snying por 'gro ba'i bkod pa kun ston pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-18: bag mchis pa ni bskal pa dpag tu ma mchis grangs ma mchis pa na mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-19: sgrub pa ni byang chub mngon par 'tshang rgya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-20: bag mchis pa ni sngar bgyi ba bgyis pa'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:96b-21: sgrub pa ni yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa chen por nye bar mchi ba'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-1: pa ni chos shin tu yongs su mya ngan las 'das par 'tshal ba ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-3: byang chub sems dpa' sgrub pa 'di lta bu dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-4: bag mchis pa 'di lta bu dang ldan pa ni byang chub rnyed par dka' ba ma lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-6: de lta bas na byang chub sems dpas sgrub pa 'di dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-7: bag mchis pa 'di la brtson par bgyi ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-9: 'di ni chos yang dag par brjod pa lags so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-10: de nas bcom ldan 'das la byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po blo gros rnam par gnon gyis 'di skad ces gsol to //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-12: 'di la byang chub sems dpa' rnams chos yang dag par 'dzin pa zhig la gnas nas sangs rgyas kyi byang chub yang dag par sgrub ste /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-13: de la kha cig ni 'di snyam du gang sangs rgyas sangs rgyas zhes bya ba 'di chos gang gi ming du sangs rgyas zhes btags snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-14: de dag de ltar rtog pa na gang 'di sangs rgyas zhes bgyi ba'i chos de dag yang dag par rjes su mi mthong ngo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-15: de dag sangs rgyas ji lta ba de bzhin du chos thams cad khong du chud do //

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97a-17: la la ni 'di snyam du sems te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:97b-0: gang @97b chos zhes bya ba'i chos 'di ni yul na mi gnas /

K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:152b-10: bdag ni sems can thams cad bsgral slad kyis bdag rgal bar 'tshal lo //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:152b-13: bsgral ba'ang ma dmigs par bgyi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:152b-14: bcom ldan 'das bdag ni de lta bu'i sems dang ldan pas chos kyi rnam grangs 'di gzungs bar bgyi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:152b-15: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pas gsol pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:152b-17: gang 'di ltar bdag gis dam pa'i chos yongs su gzung ngo snyam pa 'di ni 'jig rten gyi phyin ci9 log go //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:152b-19: byang chub sems dpas ni re zhig bdag nyid dul bar bgyi /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-0: @153a *// bdag nyid dul zhing zhi la nye bar zhi nas chos kyi ngo bo nyid kyis dam pa'i chos yongs su gzung bar rngo thogs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-2: bdag ni bdag nyid dul zhing zhi ba la nye bar zhi nas chos kyi ngo bo nyid kyis dam pa'i chos yongs su gzung bar bgyi'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-3: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa' dam pa'i chos yongs su zin pa de dag la legs so zhes bya ba byin te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-5: 'di ltar khyed cag sems can thams cad la phan pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-6: bde ba'i phyir dam pa'i chos yongs su gzung bar spro ba ni legs so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-9: dam pa'i chos yongs su 'dzin pa ni byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi yang dag phul gyi chos so //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-10: byang chub sems dpa' rtag tu dam pa'i chos yongs su gzung ba la brtson par bya'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-12: chos yang dag par brjod pa dang rab tu ldan pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs 'di gzung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-14: kun chub par byas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po ni skye ba med pa /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-15: 'gag pa med pa'i sku ni chos kyi sku'o //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-16: chos kyi sku ni sangs rgyas kyi sku'o zhes sangs rgyas la snang ba chen po thob par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153a-17: chos thams cad ni ma byas pa 'dus ma byas pa'o zhes chos la snang ba chen po thob 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-0: nga yi @153b pa med pa dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-1: yongs su 'dzin pa med pa ni bcom ldan 'das kyi slob ma'i dge 'dun no zhes dge 'dun la snang ba chen po thob par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-2: snying rje chen po ni byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa'i rtsa ba'o zhes byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa rnams la snang ba thob par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-3: nges pa'i tshig thams cad ni skye ba med pa'i ngo bo nyid do zhes spobs pa'i snang ba thob par 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-5: chos kyi rnam grangs 'di ni klu'i rgyal po rgya mtsho'i gnas dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-7: klu'i rgyal po ma dros pa'i gnas su spyod par 'gyur /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-8: de'i 'og tu dzambu'i gling du spyod par 'gyur te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-9: sems can gang dag sangs rgyas kyis yongs su gzung ba dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-10: byang chub sems dpas yongs su gzung bar 'gyur ba /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-14: chos zab mo la mos pa de dag gi lag tu 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-15: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal nas /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-16: byang chub sems dpa' rtsom pa med dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-17: byang chub sems dpa' blo gros rnam par gnon dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-18: byang chub sems dpa' de dag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-19: nyan thos chen po de dag dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-23: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rangs te /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:153b-24: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do //
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:154a-0: 'phags pa chos thams cad yang dag par sdud pa stong phrag brgya @154a *//
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:154a-2: rtsom pa med kyi le'u ste bcu gnyis pa rdzogs so ////
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:154a-3: rgya gar gyi mkhan po manydzu shr'i garbha dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:154a-4: bi dza ya sh'i la dang /
K10acip-k_lha_sa-065-001:154a-6: zhus chen gyi lo tstsha bande ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te skad gsar bcad kyis kyang bcos nas gtan la phab pa //
